<item>
            <title>[LU-10246] FLR: sanity test_205: short description of the failure</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10246</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah_lw &amp;lt;wei3.liu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/1545c6da-c96a-11e7-9840-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/1545c6da-c96a-11e7-9840-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_205 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;No jobstats for id.205.mkdir.25805 found on mds::*..job_stats
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Running sanity with the mount dir set up as&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;lfs mirror create -N2 -E 1M -E eof /mnt/lustre&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;client console&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 205: Verify job stats ================================================================= 02:51:00 (1510023060)
Waiting 90 secs for update
Updated after 10s: wanted &apos;nodelocal&apos; got &apos;nodelocal&apos;
Registered as changelog user cl7
mdt.lustre-MDT0000.job_cleanup_interval=5
jobid_name=id.205.mkdir.25805
Test: mkdir /mnt/lustre/d205.sanity
Using JobID environment variable nodelocal=id.205.mkdir.25805
onyx-71: error: get_param: param_path &apos;*//job_stats&apos;: No such file or directory
onyx-71: error: get_param: param_path &apos;*//job_stats&apos;: No such file or directory
 sanity test_205: @@@@@@ FAIL: No jobstats for id.205.mkdir.25805 found on mds::*..job_stats 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
